OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 19 Apr to Sun 3 MayFIt
OL,6,Fis probable that more blocked, or at
OL,7,Fleast slowly evolving, weather
OL,8,Fpatterns will become increasingly
OL,9,Fdominant through late April into May.
OL,10,FWhilst confidence is low, this may
OL,11,Fresult in more settled and drier
OL,12,Fconditions overall, although some more
OL,13,Funsettled interludes are still
OL,14,Fpossible at times. Temperatures will
OL,15,Fprobably be close to or above normal
OL,16,Ffor the period as a whole.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
